data.description: Better than new construction with modern finishes throughout!  This home was built just a few years ago and from the moment you step in, you'll see how well cared for this home is, and how much light it offers! The main level offers the primary suite, add'l bedroom & bath, the laundry room, a mudroom, spacious living area, dining room, and the incredible kitchen with a walk-in pantry. The kitchen (and all bathrooms) cabinets are a modern style with gorgeous quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances.  The lower level offers an add'l living space, a wet bar, 2 large bedrooms, a full bath and still great storage in the utility room.  Off the main level dining room you'll step onto the covered deck area out back that is fully fenced in, has an irrigation system and also offers an additional patio space. ****Attention VA loan eligible buyers......ask how you could purchase this home @2.5% interest rate for a decent portion of the loan.
